2:T89d,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) better than Codium AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) scores 7.0 overall while Codium AI scores 7.0. Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) is best for AWS developers and teams already in AWS ecosystem, while Codium AI excels for teams prioritizing test coverage and quality-focused development."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) or Codium AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) starts at $19/mo and Codium AI starts at $19/mo. Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) offers a free plan. Codium AI offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) to Codium AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) and Codium AI support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) vs Codium AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Codium AI has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) for free tier for individuals and Codium AI for excellent test generation."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Developer) or Codium AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Amazon CodeWhisperer (Q Devel